## 3. Call Stack Ka Flow (Kaise Kaam Karta Hai)

1. Program shuru hone pe → **Global Execution Context** stack pe push hota hai (sabse neeche)

2. Jab koi function call hota hai → **naya Function Execution Context** stack pe upar push ho jaata hai

3. Function ke andar aur function call hua → aur ek context push

4. Function khatam hua (return ya } khatam) → woh context **pop** ho jaata hai

5. Stack khali hone tak yeh chalta rahta hai

