Q: new Promise() se kya hota hai?



Answer: "new Promise() se ek Promise object create hota hai jo future value ko represent karta hai. Iske andar ek executor function hota hai jisme hum async operations karte hain. Jab operation complete ho jata hai to resolve() ya reject() call karte hain."

Q: Promise ke 3 states kya hain?



Answer:



&#x20;   Pending - Initial state, operation abhi chal raha



&#x20;   Fulfilled/Resolved - Operation successful, resolve() call hua



&#x20;   Rejected - Operation failed, reject() call hua



